metadata.name: Mesmerizing
metadata.description:
Painted on handmade rice paper in the Chinese Brush Painting tradition with ink and silver, the ink chrysanthemum represents fidelity and rebirth.
 
“With all of the time in the world to spend it
Wild and unwise, I want to be mesmerizing too
Mesmerizing too
Mesmerizing to, you”
Liz Phair, Mesmerizing
